various development tools:

create_qtcreator_files.sh	- create *.files for qtcreator
valgrind-suppressions		- known problems when testing
				  with valgrind memcheck/leakcheck
				  
build systems:

osc				- OpenSuse Build Service specific stuff
ArchLinux                       - PKGBUILD for builds on ArchLinux
redhat                          - local build script for RHEL

FreeBSD                         - FreeBSD ports and patches
Solaris                         - Solaris ports and patches
Windows                         - Windows patches
